# Format of each line is:
#	devicename : deviceaddress : variable <space>  comment
# If the comment begins with a '(H)', the device is hidden from the web view
# This file is automatically edited by genweb.cgi (or snipsweb.cgi) so
# it should be writable by your httpd process.

